item.description:
I have a custom Twig function that will output a question mark icon with tooltipfunctionality from bootstrap. My Symfony twig extension class looks like this:
public function getFunctions()
{
return array(
new \Twig_SimpleFunction(
'tooltip_icon',
array($this, 'tooltipIcon'),
array('is_safe' =&gt; array('html'))
),
);
}
